- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is relevant as the paper uses distributional representations of documents. 
- cs.IR (Information Retrieval) is relevant as the paper evaluates the effectiveness of the proposed algorithm in capturing political dimensions in text. 
- cs.CY (Computers and Society) is less likely but still possible as the paper deals with political text and its analysis.
